  "time_ut": 1659417466,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dba \u0d85\u0dc4\u0ddd\u0dc3\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dc0 \u0dc0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d95\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A new constitution is needed to abolish the executive presidency",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Justice Minister Wijayadasa Rajapaksa said that if the executive presidency is to be abolished completely, a new constitution should be brought in place of the existing constitution. He also mentioned that the basis of the current constitution is the executive presidential system."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
